{"id":22704,"type":2,"name":"Le Roi et l'oiseau","name_cn":"国王与小鸟","date":"1980-03-19","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/db/da/22704_QRrQ3.jpg","rating":{"rank":942,"total":73,"count":{"1":1,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":1,"6":7,"7":22,"8":23,"9":12,"10":7},"score":7.7},"summary":"本片改编自安徒生童话《牧羊女和扫烟囱的工人》。国王密室的墙壁上画着一位美丽的牧羊姑娘和一个扫烟囱的小伙子。两人坠入爱河，相约从画中出来，并在一只聪明的小鸟的帮助下逃出了王宫。但是国王的画像也活了过来。国王不但掳走了牧羊姑娘，又把扫烟囱的小伙子和小鸟一起打入地牢。最终小鸟和地下的义民一起推翻了残暴的国王，救出了牧羊姑娘。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>国王与小鸟</li><li><span>话数: </span>1</li><li><span>原作: </span><a href=\"/person/2496\">Hans Christian Andersen</a></li><li><span>上映年度: </span>1980年3月19日</li><li><span>片长: </span>87分钟</li><li><span>官方网站: </span>http://www.paulgrimault.com/</li>","collection":{"on_hold":10,"dropped":8,"wish":73,"collect":101,"doing":4},"tags":[{"name":"法国","count":30},{"name":"1980","count":23},{"name":"剧场版","count":15},{"name":"欧美","count":14},{"name":"动画电影","count":10},{"name":"爱情","count":6},{"name":"经典","count":3},{"name":"电影","count":3},{"name":"冒险","count":3},{"name":"80年代","count":2},{"name":"动画","count":2},{"name":"七分","count":1},{"name":"映画","count":1},{"name":"原创","count":1},{"name":"","count":""}],"eps":[{"id":123377,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/123377","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":1,"desc":""}],"staff":[{"id":2496,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/12/ff/2496_prsn_anidb.jpg","name":"Hans Christian Andersen","desc":"原作"}]}